<br>
Out of the 4 pure casters, Magicians are probably the weakest at dueling at lvl 60. Yes even Enchanters can kill us (even if we had decent MR).<br>
<br>
I have no clue how you guys are beating those Wizards...because in all honesty, it doesn't even require that much skill for a Wizard to beat a Magician in a duel. Kleanboy you said you have 100% hp and your pet has 100% hp left after the duel...what is this? Are you sure the Wizards wasn't afk? It just sounds purely &quot;wishful thinking&quot; to me. And the part about you beating lvl 60 epic Wizards...what? The Rune from their Epic owns so much the Wizard should be able to beat you with 100% hp left. And Dimented - no offense but it sounds like you've never dueled a Wizard. First off pet will NOT interrupt the Wizard's casting much (even I can resist ALL of Air pet's stuns in a duel, and pet's bash only *sometimes* work). By the time you get Mala off the wizard would have rooted your pet and starting to cast on YOU. All they need is less than 10 seconds to land 2-3 nukes to kill you, in the main time you'll be hard pressed to get out even 2 nukes (and no, 2 mage nukes can't kill a Wizard, while 2-3 Wizard nukes can kill a mage). Plus they get so many fast casting stuns, if they want to they could just interrupt you. <br>
<br>
